                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221204-70-off377 t18221204-70-crimeloc380"></join>. On the 28th of November, between two and three o'clock, a boy called me - I went, and laid hold of the prisoner at the door; two baskets and a saucepan were found on her, which were taken from the front cellar. She must have come into the house to take them. One basket belonged to 
               <persName id="t18221204-70-person611">
